$Id: README,v 1.1 2002/11/20 18:20:15 reggers Exp reggers $

This module, Apache::AuthenFTP, is an Apache/mod_perl authentication handler
to authenticate users using a FTP server (or anything that implements the
authentication phase of the FTP service).

To build and install it, please run

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

To read more about this module try

    pod2text AuthenFTP.pm

